    "en": {
      "title": "Petrol can be supplied at Rs 250",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Looking at the fuel price in the world market, we can supply petrol domestically for 250 rupees a liter, MP Sampika Ranavaka said.",
        "Although the price of fuel in the world market has increased massively in the past, the price of Perel has decreased from 120 dollars to 90 dollars, he said."
      ],
